{"name":"route","desc":"该命令用于在Linux计算机网络中查看和修改路由表。它可以显示当前路由表的内容，添加或删除路由表项以及设置默认网关。","noMergeOptions":true,"usages":[{"name":"查看路由表","form":{},"filter":"(cmd) => cmd + ' -n'"},{"name":"添加静态路由","form":{"net":{"name":"目标网络","desc":"例如：192.168.10.0","required":true,"type":"string"},"netmask":{"name":"子网掩码","desc":"例如：255.255.255.0","required":true,"type":"string"},"gw":{"name":"网关","desc":"例如：192.168.10.1","required":true,"type":"string"},"dev":{"name":"设备","desc":"例如：eth0","required":true,"type":"string"}},"optionsPartFilter":"(cmd, values) => `add ${cmd} -net ${values.net} netmask ${values.netmask} gw ${values.gw} dev ${values.dev}`"},{"name":"删除静态路由","form":{"net":{"name":"目标网络","desc":"例如：192.168.10.0","required":true,"type":"string"},"netmask":{"name":"子网掩码","desc":"例如：255.255.255.0","required":true,"type":"string"},"gw":{"name":"网关","desc":"例如：192.168.10.1","required":true,"type":"string"},"dev":{"name":"设备","desc":"例如：eth0","required":true,"type":"string"}},"optionsPartFilter":"(cmd, values) => `del ${cmd} -net ${values.net} netmask ${values.netmask} gw ${values.gw} dev ${values.dev}`"},{"name":"添加默认网关","form":{"gw":{"name":"网关","desc":"例如：192.168.10.1","required":true,"type":"string"},"dev":{"name":"设备","desc":"例如：eth0","required":true,"type":"string"}},"optionsPartFilter":"(cmd, values) => `add ${cmd} default gw ${values.gw} dev ${values.dev}`"}],"content":"<h2 id=\"注意\">注意</h2>\n<p>请注意，自 Linux 内核版本 4.20 起，route 命令已被 ip route 命令所取代。ip route 命令提供了更多的功能和灵活性，因此建议在较新的 Linux 系统上使用 ip route 命令来管理路由表。</p>\n<h2 id=\"例子\">例子</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>显示当前路由表项：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>route -n\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>添加一条新路由：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>route add -net 192.168.0.0 netmask 255.255.255.0 gw 192.168.1.1\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>删除一条路由表项：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>route del -net 192.168.0.0 netmask 255.255.255.0\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>设置默认网关：</li>\n</ul>\n<pre><code>route add default gw 192.168.1.1\n</code></pre>\n"}